text: Tottenham Hotspur F.C. Women, or just Tottenham or Spurs for short, is an English women's football club with connections to the Tottenham Hotspur F.C. men's football club. The club currently plays in the Women's Super League (or WSL for short), the top football division of women's football in England. It was created in 1985. Category:Tottenham Hotspur F.C.
